A word or two about memory
**************************

   MechForce is a huge program. If your system has only 512K of memory
you will be limited in the number of mechs you can load. Computer mechs
take a lot more memory than player mechs. You will probably be able to
load 24 to 32 player mechs, but if you are playing against the computer
8 player and 8 computer will probably be the limit. If your load too
many mechs there will not be enough memory left to load the sound files.


@EndNode

